        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer402842801" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer7560490062398459957">Probably my favorite book ever written. The &apos;waves&apos; become a compound metaphor of sheer brilliance; we are all a harmony in the chorus of life, a part of a whole but each an individual part of beauty equally beautiful in solidarity as the whole. I wish I could write a single sentence as glorious as Woolf. </span>
  <span id="freeText7560490062398459957" style="display:none">Probably my favorite book ever written. The 'waves' become a compound metaphor of sheer brilliance; we are all a harmony in the chorus of life, a part of a whole but each an individual part of beauty equally beautiful in solidarity as the whole. I wish I could write a single sentence as glorious as Woolf. </span>
